Please make sure we communicate that you only thave 2 alliance partners, but three allince opponents, the ratio should NOT be 50/50 with any given team as a result.

Also the match maker has absolutely ZERO knowledge of team strength. If you think you are pared up against a powerhouse team more often and think that something weird is happening you are likely experiencing a combination of the 2partners/3 opponents bias and proportionally bias.

Alright, for my own sanity I hope this is the last update:

plotter.py consolidates the other two and asks if you want Matches With and/or Against as well as Elims and Quals.

An output folder will now be created with the filestructure: output(teamnumber)\ and then the png and HTML files for offline viewing or just saving in general.

They’re named for the selected options, eg. qfMaMw1997-2024

q = Quals
f = Elims
Ma = Matches Against
Mw = Matches With
